Roger Maxwell (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Maxwell_(actor) 0 Roger Maxwell (1 January 1900 – 24 November 1971) was an English actor.In 1959, he was a member of the jury at the Venice Film Festival.Maxwell was born in London, England and died in London also.
